                    </a>
                    at line <b><?= $e->getLine(); ?></b>.
                </i>

                <span class="time">
                    Exception thrown in <strong><?= self::getExceptionTime(); ?></strong>.
                </span>

                <?php $code = self::highlight($e->getFile(), $e->getLine(), 10); ?>

